---
title: 'Deluxe Pizza' Pasta with Cheesy Garlic Toast
description: Deluxe pizza lovers rejoice! We've taken your favourite pizza and given it the pasta makeover to create the DELUXE PASTA! Fitting to the name, this pasta features crisp green peppers, umami-rich mushrooms, Italian sausage, marinara sauce and some shredded mozzarella for good measure! Accept no substitutes! Unless it's this pasta dish, of course.
